\v 1 Umpristi omkhulu wasesithi: Kambe lezizinto zinjalo?
\v 2 Wasesithi: Madoda, bazalwane labobaba, lalelani\x + 22.1.\x*. UNkulunkulu wenkazimulo wabonakala kubaba wethu uAbrahama eseMesopotamiya\x + 2.9.\x*, engakahlali eHarani\x + Gen. 11.31. Gen. 12.1.\x*,
