\v 5 kodwa kamnikanga ilifa kilo, hatshi lanyathela\x + 7.43.\x*; kodwa wathembisa ukumnika lona libe ngelakhe, lelenzalo yakhe emva kwakhe\x + Gen. 12.7. 13.15. 15.3,18. 17.8.\x*, enga\add ka\add*bi lamntwana\x + Gen. 15.3. 18.10.\x*.
\v 6 UNkulunkulu wasekhuluma kanje esithi inzalo yakhe izakuba yisihambi elizweni lemzini, bazayenza isigqili baza\add yi\add*phatha kubi\x + Gen. 15.13,14.\x*, iminyaka engamakhulu amane\x + 7.17. Eks. 12.40.\x*;
\v 7 kodwa lesosizwe, abazakuba yizigqili kuso, ngizasigweba mina, kutsho uNkulunkulu; njalo emva kwalezizinto bazaphuma, bangikhonze kulindawo\x + Eks. 3.12.\x*.
\v 8 Wasemnika isivumelwano sokusoka\x + Gen. 17.9-12.\x*; ngokunjalo wazala uIsaka, wamsoka ngosuku lwesificaminwembili\x + Gen. 21.2-4.\x*; loIsaka \add wazala\add* uJakobe\x + Gen. 25.26.\x*, loJakobe\x + Gen. 29.31-35. 30.5-24. 35.18,23-26.\x* okhokho abalitshumi lambili\x + 2.29.\x*.
\v 9 Okhokho\x + 2.29.\x* basebesiba lomona\x + 17.5.\x* bathengisa uJosefa eGibhithe\x + Gen. 37.4,11,28. Hlab. 105.17.\x*; kodwa uNkulunkulu wayelaye\x + Gen. 39.2,21,23.\x*,
\v 10 wasemkhulula kuzo zonke inhlupheko zakhe, wamnika umusa lenhlakanipho phambi kukaFaro inkosi yeGibhithe; wasembeka ukuba ngumbusi phezu kweGibhithe lowendlu yakhe yonke\x + Gen. 41.37,40. 42.6. Hlab. 105.21.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekufika indlala elizweni lonke leGibhithe leleKhanani, lokuhlupheka okukhulu; labobaba bethu kabatholanga ukudla\x + Gen. 41.54.\x*.
\v 12 Kodwa uJakobe esezwile ukuthi kukhona amabele eGibhithe, wathuma obaba bethu okokuqala\x + Gen. 42.1-3.\x*.
\v 13 Kwathi ngokwesibili\x + Gen. 43.15.\x* uJosefa waziswa kubafowabo\x + Gen. 45.4.\x*, labakibo kaJosefa babonakaliswa kuFaro\x + Gen. 45.16.\x*.
\v 14 UJosefa wasethumela wabizela kuye uyise uJakobe\x + Gen. 45.9,27.\x*, lalo lonke usendo lwakhe\x + Gen. 46.27. Eks. 1.5. Dute. 10.22.\x*, kulemiphefumulo\x + 27.37.\x* engamatshumi ayisikhombisa lanhlanu\x + Gen. 46.26. Gen. 38.12. 46.10,20.\x*.
\v 15 UJakobe wasesehlela eGibhithe\x + Gen. 46.5,28.\x*, wasesifa yena\x + Gen. 49.33.\x* labobaba bethu\x + Eks. 1.6.\x*;
\v 16 basebethwalelwa\x + Gen. 50.25. Eks. 13.19.\x* eShikemi\x + Josh. 17.7. Joha. 4.5.\x*, balaliswa engcwabeni uAbrahama ayelithenge ngentengo yemali\x + Gen. 23.16. Gen. 33.19.\x* kumadodana kaHamori\x + Josh. 24.32.\x*\x + Gen. 23.16. Gen. 33.19.\x* weShikemi\x + Gen. 33.19. Josh. 24.32.\x*.
\v 17 Kwathi sesisondele isikhathi sesithembiso uNkulunkulu ayesifunge kuAbrahama\x + Gen. 15.13,16. Seb. 7.6.\x*, bakhula abantu banda eGibhithe\x + Eks. 1.7. Hlab. 105.24. Seb. 13.17.\x*,
\v 18 kwaze kwavela enye inkosi, eyayingamazi uJosefa\x + Eks. 1.8.\x*.
\v 19 Yona yasiphatha ngobuqili isizukulu sakithi, yabahlupha obaba bethu\x + Eks. 1.10. Hlab. 105.25.\x*, ukubalahlisa insane zabo\x + Eks. 1.22.\x*, ukuze zingaphili\x + Eks. 1.17,18,22. Luka 17.33.\x*.
\v 20 Ngalesosikhathi kwazalwa uMozisi\x + Eks. 2.2.\x*, waba muhle kuNkulunkulu; owondliwa endlini kayise inyanga ezintathu\x + Eks. 2.2. Heb. 11.23.\x*.
\v 21 Eselahliwe, indodakazi kaFaro yamdobha, yazondlela yena ukuthi abe yindodana\x + Eks. 2.3-10.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo uMozisi wafundiswa kuyo yonke inhlakanipho yamaGibhithe\x + 1 Kho. 4.30.\x*; wasesiba lamandla ngamazwi langemisebenzi\x + Luka 24.19.\x*.
\v 23 Kwathi eselesikhathi seminyaka engamatshumi amane agcweleyo, kwafika enhliziyweni yakhe\x + 1 Kor. 2.9. Luka 24.38.\x* ukuthi ahambele abafowabo abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 2.11,12.\x*.
\v 24 Kwathi ebona omunye ephathwa kubi, wa\add m\add*vikela wamphindisela ohlutshwayo, watshaya umGibhithe;
\v 25 njalo wayethemba ukuthi abafowabo bazaqedisisa ukuthi uNkulunkulu ubanika inkululeko ngesandla sakhe; kodwa kabaqedisisanga.
\v 26 Njalo ngosuku olulandelayo wazibonakalisa kibo ababesilwa, wabalamula ngamandla, esithi: Madoda, lingabazalwane; liphathanelani kubi\x + Eks. 2.13,14.\x*?
\v 27 Kodwa lowo owayemona umakhelwane wamsunduza, esithi: Ubekwe ngubani ukuba ngumbusi lomahluleli phezu kwethu?
\v 28 Usufuna ukungibulala yini, njengoba ubulele umGibhithe izolo\x + Luka 12.14.\x*?
\v 29 Ngalelilizwi uMozisi wasebaleka, waba ngowemzini elizweni leMadiyani\x + Eks. 2.15.\x*, lapho azala khona amadodana amabili\x + Eks. 2.22. 4.20. 18.3,4.\x*.
\v 30 Kwathi sekugcwaliseke iminyaka engamatshumi amane, kwabonakala kuye enkangala\x + Eks. 3.2.\x* yentaba iSinayi ingilosi yeNkosi phakathi kwelangabi lomlilo esihlahleni\x + Eks. 3.1.\x*.
\v 31 Kwathi uMozisi esebonile wamangala ngalowombono; esasondela ukuthi akhangelisise, ilizwi leNkosi lafika kuye \add lisithi\x + 7.32. Luka 12.24,27. Heb. 3.1.\x*\add*:
\v 32 Mina nginguNkulunkulu waboyihlo, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama loNkulunkulu kaIsaka loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + Eks. 3.6.\x*. UMozisi wasethuthumela\x + Eks. 3.6.\x*, kazaba lesibindi sokukhangelisisa\x + 7.32. Luka 12.24,27. Heb. 3.1.\x*.
\v 33 INkosi yasisithi kuye: Khulula amanyathela enyaweni zakho; ngoba indawo omi kiyo ingumhlabathi ongcwele\x + Eks. 3.5. So Josh. 5.15.\x*.
\v 34 Ngikubonile lokukubona ukuhlutshwa kwabantu bami abaseGibhithe, njalo ngizwile ukububula kwabo; sengehlile ukuthi ngibakhulule; khathesi-ke woza, ngizakuthuma eGibhithe\x + Eks. 3.7,8,10.\x*.
\v 35 UMozisi lo abamalayo besithi: Ubekwe ngubani ukuba ngumbusi lomahluleli? - nguye uNkulunkulu amthumayo ukuba ngumbusi lomkhululi ngesandla sengilosi eyabonakala kuye esihlahleni\x + Nani 20.16.\x*.
\v 36 Yena wabakhupha\x + Eks. 12.41. 33.1.\x*, esenze izimangaliso lezibonakaliso elizweni leGibhithe\x + Eks. 7. 1. 11. 1. Hlab. 105.27-36. Joha. 4.48.\x* loLwandle oluBomvu\x + Eks. 14.21,27-31.\x*, lenkangala\x + Eks. 16.1,35. 17.1-6.\x* iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 13.18.\x*.
\v 37 Nguye lowo uMozisi owathi kubantwana bakoIsrayeli: INkosi uNkulunkulu wenu uzalivusela umprofethi kubazalwane benu onjengami; lizamuzwa yena\x + Dute. 18.15. Seb. 3.22.\x*.
\v 38 Nguye lowo\x + Eks. 19.3,17.\x* owayesebandleni enkangala\x + 1 Lan. 13.2.\x*, kanye lengilosi eyakhuluma laye entabeni iSinayi kanye labobaba bethu\x + Isa. 63.9. Seb. 7.53.\x*; owemukela\x + Joha. 1.17.\x* amazwi aphilayo\x + Roma 3.2.\x*, ukuze asinike;
\v 39 yena obaba bethu abangavumanga ukumlalela, kodwa ba\add m\add*sunduzela eceleni, basebebuyela eGibhithe ngenhliziyo zabo\x + Eks. 16.3.\x*,
\v 40 besithi kuAroni: Senzele onkulunkulu abazahamba phambi kwethu; ngoba uMozisi lo, owasikhupha elizweni iGibhithe, kasazi ukuthi wehlelwe yini\x + Eks. 32.1.\x*.
\v 41 Basebesenza ithole ngalezonsuku\x + Eks. 32.4-6. Hlab. 106.19.\x*, baletha umhlatshelo esithombeni\x + Eks. 32.4-6. Hlab. 106.19.\x*, bajabula\x + Amos 6.13.\x* ngemisebenzi yezandla zabo\x + Jer. 1.16.\x*.
\v 42 Kodwa uNkulunkulu wafulathela\x + Josh. 24.20.\x*, wabanikela ukuthi bakhonze\x + Hlab. 81.12. Hez. 20.39.\x* ibutho lezulu\x + Jer. 19.13. Dute. 4.19. Luka 2.13.\x*; njengokulotshiweyo encwadini yabaprofethi \add ukuthi\add*: Laletha kimi yini imihlatshelo leminikelo iminyaka engamatshumi amane enkangala, ndlu kaIsrayeli\x + Amos 5.25-27.\x*?
\v 43 Njalo lathatha ithabhanekele likaMoloki lenkanyezi kankulunkulu wenu uRefani, imifanekiso elayenza ukuthi liyikhonze\x + 1 Kho. 11.7.\x*; njalo ngizalithuthela ngaphambili kweBhabhiloni\x + 7.4.\x*.
\v 44 Obaba bethu babelalo ithabhanekele lobufakazi enkangala\x + Nani 17.7.\x*, njengokulayela kwalowo owakhuluma loMozisi, ukuthi alenze ngomfanekiso ayewubonile\x + Eks. 25.40.\x*;
